1 Cucumber
1 sprig Spring Onion
1 Lemon
4 The Everything Bagel
1 packet Cream Cheese

Thinly slice cucumber. Thinly
slice spring onion. Cut lemon
into wedges.

Halve the everything bagels.
Toast or grill to you liking.

Transfer bagels to serving
plates. Spread with some
cream cheese and top with
cucumber, spring onions and
a squeeze of lemon juice.
Season with salt and pepper.
Serve with remaining lemon
wedges.